  <titleInfo>
    <title>Children in Adult Jails: A Report</title>
  </titleInfo>
  <abstract>This report focuses on a large number of children subjected to violation of their rights and well-being through jail incarceration. It seeks to determine why children are jailed, which children are placed behind bars, and what happens to children in jails.</abstract>
